lead_paragraph: Cristie Kerr has bagged more than $17.5 million in career earnings, won two majors and three times occupied top spot in the world rankings but this season has been an 'annus horribilis' for the American.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Longest Club Is Driving Sad Kerr to Distraction
